Version:        1.3
License:        LGPL
License-file:   LICENSE
Author:         John Meacham <john at repetae dot net>
                Tuomo Valkonen <tuomov at iki.fi>
                Don Stewart <http://www.cse.unsw.edu.au/~dons>
                Stefan Wehr <http://www.informatik.uni-freiburg.de/~wehr/>
